_sText: I made this map, Is fun and there is lots of good shooting places. Both teams has samekind areas, only defference is ground, and the areas are mirrored, not rotated. There is invisible wall, so you cant rush ;) (LIE!!!) Hope you like it =] The wall in center must be shot 3 times with awp, or 4-6 times with deagle. This wall is there because i hate spawn killers :) Here is the darker version (night) of this map. Some water added too.. awp_minicastle_night
